{{Infobox newspaper | name =Monaco Hebdo | logo = | image = | caption = | format = | foundation = 1995 | owners = [[Caroli Group]] | political = | language = French | headquarters = | editor = | website = [http://www.monacohebdo.mc/ monacohebdo.mc] | ISSN = }} '''Monaco Hebdo''' is a weekly newspaper in [[Monaco]].<ref name=listesycom>{{cite web|title=Liste des Médias en Principauté de Monaco (2015)|url=http://www.sycom.mc/medias-monaco.html|website=Sycom (Services d’information et de communication institutionnels en Principauté de Monaco)|accessdate=December 20, 2015}}</ref> It was established in September 1995.<ref name=caroli>{{cite web|title=Le journal d’information MONACO HEBDO|url=http://caroli-realestate.com/fr/presentation|website=Caroli Group|accessdate=December 20, 2015}}</ref> As of 2007, it had a circulation of 3,000.<ref name=parliamentary>{{cite book|title=Parliamentary Assembly, Working Papers: 2007 Ordinary Session (Third Part) 25-29 June 2007|date=January 30, 2008|publisher=Council of Europe|page=281|accessdate=December 20, 2015}}</ref> It is published by the [[Caroli Group]].<ref name=caroli/>
